The pattern for skills is as follows:

Filename should be skill name (Case sensitive)
In file:-

Skill Name
Description
Macro name (with respect to root_game_folder/data/macros)
Activation Codes (0-On start of turn, 1-Just before attack (Temporary), 2-End of Turn, 4-When Played, 3-When dead, 5-When opposite card dies,6-When taking attack damage,7-when taking magic damage,8-Just after attacking,9-Just after magic attack,10-When taking damage from range [eg. magic/status effects]),11-When any team card takes physical damage
Target Code (See Skill.java file)
Is negatable? (Y/N)
Activates in absence of opponent in front? (Y/N) (0=N,1=Y)
